<body>
<div class="wrapper">

  <main>

      <section class="module parallax parallax-1">
        <div class="container">
          <h1>Bates</h1>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="module content">
        <div class="container">
          <h2>Bates College Virtual Tour</h2>
          <p>Bates College is a small liberal arts school in Lewiston, Maine.</p>
          <p>Please enjoy the following virtual tour of Commons Dining Hall and Hedge Hall.  Click on the spaces to navigate through them and immerse yourselves with recorded lectures, pictures, and additional information about life at Bates.</p>
          <iframe width=100% height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/opKhbPguFfY?autoplay=1&controls=0&showinfo=0&rel=0&loop=1" frameborder="0" gesture="media" allowfullscreen class="video"></iframe>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="module parallax parallax-2">
        <div class="container">
          <h1>College</h1>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="module content">
        <div class="container">
          <h2>Commons Dining Hall</h2>
          <p>Below is a walking tour of our beautiful Commons Dining Hall.  Please, walk through, click on tags, and fully immerse yourself.</p>
          <center><iframe width='853' height='480' src='https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=2a9zku8EDco' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen></iframe></center>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="module parallax parallax-3">
        <div class="container">
          <h1>Virtual</h1>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="module content">
        <div class="container">
          <h2>Hedge Hall</h2>
          <p>Below is a walking tour of Hedge Hall.  Hedge Hall is an academic building on campus home to philosophy, environmental studies and religious studies. Please, walk through, click on tags, and fully immerse yourself.</p>
          <center><iframe width='853' height='480' src='https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=TuWm6t4UNq9' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen></iframe></center>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="module parallax parallax-4">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Campus</h1>
        </div>
      </section>

      <footer>
          <div class="copyright">
              <center><p>Independent Study: Virtual Tour of Bates</p></center>

          </div>


  </main><!-- /main -->
<!-- /footer -->

</div><!-- /#wrapper -->

